info.name: InterPayTollApi
info.description:
The REST API is designed to manage toll station interoperability data. It supports operations for storing and retrieving information, adhering to the following base URL:

**Base URL:** `https://{{host}}:9115/api`

All API endpoints are structured as:  
`{baseURL}/{service}/{path-to-resource}`

Data formats supported: JSON (`application/json`) and CSV (`text/csv`). The default format is JSON if not specified.
